      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s in such incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, and the interior is still spotless. It drives like a total dream, and I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
