    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving Bavarian engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is centered around a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission delivering power through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. This specimen is mechanically impeccable: the rod bearing service has been performed, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension maintains factory-spec geometry with no bushing compliance issues, offering telepathic turn-in. Finished in collector-grade condition, this vehicle underwent a recent compression test with stellar results across all six cylinders. A purist\u2019s dream with zero deferred maintenance.",
